                                <h2><a href="/en/activities/2024/state-funeral-events-right-honourable-brian-mulroney">State funeral events for the Right Honourable Brian Mulroney</a></h2>            </div>
          </div>
                          <div class="row media-center-search-body hidden-xs">
            <div class="col-md-12"><p>Governor General Mary Simon and Mr. Whit Fraser took part in commemorative events to mark the passing of the Right Honourable Brian Mulroney P.C., C.C., G.O.Q.</p></div>
