            <div class="col-md-12">      
                                    <p class="title_prefix"><span property="dc:date dc:created" content="2024-03-21T16:25:40-04:00" datatype="xsd:dateTime"><span class="date-display-single" property="dc:date" datatype="xsd:dateTime" content="2024-03-21T00:00:00-04:00">March 21, 2024</span></span></p>
                                <h2><a href="/en/activities/2024/meritorious-service-decorations-civil-division-march-21-2024">Meritorious Service Decorations (Civil Division) - March 21, 2024</a></h2>            </div>
          </div>
                          <div class="row media-center-search-body hidden-xs">
            <div class="col-md-12"><p>Governor General Mary Simon presented a total of 64 Meritorious Service Decorations (Civil Division), including 8 Meritorious Service Crosses (M.S.C.) and 56 Meritorious Service Medals (M.S.M.), during a ceremony at Rideau Hall on Thursday, March 21.</p></div>
          </div>
                </div>
