                                    <p class="title_prefix"><span property="dc:date dc:created" content="2024-04-22T13:27:53-04:00" datatype="xsd:dateTime"><span class="date-display-single" property="dc:date" datatype="xsd:dateTime" content="2024-04-22T00:00:00-04:00">April 22, 2024</span></span></p>
                                <h2><a href="/en/activities/2024/official-visit-saskatchewan">Official visit to Saskatchewan</a></h2>            </div>
          </div>
                          <div class="row media-center-search-body hidden-xs">
            <div class="col-md-12"><p>Governor General Mary Simon and Mr. Whit Fraser undertook an official visit to Saskatchewan from April 22 to 24, 2024.</p></div>
