                                <h2><a href="/en/activities/2024/official-visit-nunavut">Official visit to Nunavut</a></h2>            </div>
          </div>
                          <div class="row media-center-search-body hidden-xs">
            <div class="col-md-12"><p>Governor General Mary Simon and Mr. Whit Fraser completed an official visit to Nunavut where they marked the territory’s 25th anniversary. In Iqaluit and Qikiqtarjuaq, the Governor General met with territorial dignitaries, municipal leaders, Elders and youth.</p></div>
